These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-1::.
There 7 different types of food: banana, carrot, plum, raspberry, potato, pomegranate, nectarine
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, subway, snowmobile, helicopter, bike, van, boat
 1. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
 2. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
 3. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 4. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
 5. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
 6. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 7. the person eating carrot is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
11. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
12. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
13. the person eating pomegranate is in the middle##1
14. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person eating plum##5
15. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5
16. the person driving the bike is not the person eating nectarine##6
17. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
18. the person driving the subway is not the person eating plum##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7      |
| Nationality   | banana | raspberry | potato | pomegranate | nectarine | plum | carrot |
| Pet           | helicopter   | van    | boat       | bus     | snowmobile    | bike   | subway |

