.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-2::.
There 7 different types of food: pomegranate, banana, apricot, corn, nectarine, mango, watermelon
7 different pets are kept: pony, rat, hedgehog, snake, frog, ferret, mouse
 1. the owner of the snake is not the person eating banana##6
 2. the owner of the frog is not the person eating banana##6
 3. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
 4. the person eating corn is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
 6. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
 7. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
 9. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the right of the person eating banana##5
10. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
11. the person eating apricot is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
12. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
13. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
14. the person eating corn is the owner of the ferret##1
15. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person eating corn##1
16. the person eating nectarine is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
17. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person eating corn##1
18. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
19. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
20. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
21. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |    5     |   6    |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | apricot    | mango     | corn     | watermelon | banana      | nectarine    | pomegranate |
| Nationality   | pony | frog | ferret | hedgehog | rat | snake | mouse      |

