 3. the person drinking fanta is not the owner of the rat##6
 4. the person drinking fanta is not the owner of the goat##6
 5. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
 6. the owner of the fish is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
 9. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
11. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
12. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
13. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
14. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
15. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
16. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |     5     |     6      |     7     |
