City: nizza, prague, colone, hannover, venice, rome, miami
 1. the person who likes yellow is in an odd position##4
 2. the person traveling to prague is in an odd position##4
 3. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
 4. the person who likes azure is not the person traveling to prague##6
 5. the person traveling to venice is in the middle##1
 6. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
 7. the person who likes emerald is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to nizza##5
 9. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person who likes chestnut##5
10. the person traveling to miami is not the person who likes chestnut##6
11. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
12. the person who likes azure is in an even position##4
13. the person traveling to nizza is not the person who likes apricot##6
14. the person traveling to hannover is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who likes emerald##2
15. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
16. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |      3       |    4    |       5       |         6          |      7      |
