10. the person who likes emerald is in the middle##1
11. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
12. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
13. the person who likes black is not the person playing billiard##6
14. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
15. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
