.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-16::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: snowboarding, weightlifting, skiing, parkour, sailing, cycling, handball
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: zinnia, sunflower, rose, dahlia, azalea, tulip, daffodil
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5
 2. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
 3. the person who growsdaffodil is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
 4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who growssunflower and the person who growsdaffodil##2
 9. the person who growsrose is in an even position##4
10. the person who growsazalea is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5
11. the person who growsazalea is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is handball##2
12. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
13. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
14. the person who growssunflower is the person who's sport is handball##1
15. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaffodil##5
16. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
17. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |     4      |      5       |    6    |       7        |
| Job           | parkour    | snowboarding     | weightlifting | skiing | handball | sailing | cycling |
| Nationality   | tulip | dahlia | daffodil     | rose   | sunflower      | azalea  | zinnia      |

