.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-20::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, tram, subway, trike, snowmobile, quad-bike, bus
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, western, disaster, spy, romance, sports, adventure
 1. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 2. the person watching adventure movies is not the person driving the quad-bike##6
 3. the person driving the motorbike is between the person watching superhero movies and the person driving the tram##2
 4. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
 7. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the left of the person driving the tram##5
10. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
11. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
13. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3    |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | subway | bus   | tram  | motorbike     | snowmobile | trike    | quad-bike |
| Hobby      | sports     | spy | disaster | romance | superhero  | adventure | western |

 